OL,3,CHospital needs to cut millions this
OL,4,Cyear to balance the books
OL,6,FThe NHS Trust that runs Derriford
OL,7,FHospital needs to make cuts of nearly
OL,8,F#70 million this year as it tries to
OL,9,Fbalance the books.
OL,11,FHospital bosses said they are looking
OL,12,Fat a plan that will increase
OL,13,Fproductivity and reduce the wage bill
OL,14,Ffor staff.
OL,16,FAround half of the savings - #34
OL,17,Fmillion - will come from cutting
OL,18,Fthings like overtime, agency workers,
OL,19,Fand better management of sickness.
