OL,3,CHospital needs to cut millions this
OL,4,Cyear to balance the books
OL,6,FThe hospital has not needed to make a
OL,7,Fsaving of this size before and bosses
OL,8,Fsaid it is because of a tough
OL,9,Ffinancial climate and an increasingly
OL,10,Fstretched budget.
OL,12,FLast year the trust had to make
OL,13,Fsavings of #56 million and it said
OL,14,Fwhile it has to go a bit further this
OL,15,Fyear, it believed it can achieve that
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,FUnions today said it would have an
OL,19,Fimpact on the care the hospital offers.
