OL,3,CHospital needs to cut millions this
OL,4,Cyear to balance the books
OL,6,FKevin Treweeks, branch secretary of
OL,7,FPlymouth UNISON, said: "It's the
OL,8,Fpatients that will suffer ultimately.
OL,9,FI don't see how you can take that much
OL,10,Fstaff out of the system and it not
OL,11,Faffect patient care.
OL,13,F"It will take people who are doing the
OL,14,Fcleaning, it will take people who are
OL,15,Ffeeding the patients and will take
OL,16,Fpeople who are making the appointments
OL,17,Fand making sure this place runs
OL,18,Fsmoothly.
OL,20,F"It's going to hit every part of the
OL,21,Fservice, I'm quite sure."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
