OL,3,CHospital needs to cut millions this
OL,4,Cyear to balance the books
OL,6,FThe MP for Plymouth, Sutton and
OL,7,FDevonport, Luke Pollard, wants the
OL,8,Ftrust to move away from relying on
OL,9,Fshort-term staff and that savings like
OL,10,Fthis would better protect the hospital
OL,11,Fin future.
OL,13,FHe said: "For it to be a sustainable,
OL,14,Fgood hospital for our city, we need it
OL,15,Fto make sure it's got the right amount
OL,16,Fof investment coming in, the right
OL,17,Famount of staff, and the right staff
OL,18,Fon right contracts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
