OL,3,CHospital needs to cut millions this
OL,4,Cyear to balance the books
OL,6,F"I want to see more NHS staff on good
OL,7,FNHS contracts, not relying on the
OL,8,Ftemporary staff that the NHS has
OL,9,Fbecome so addicted to to manage the
OL,10,Fcrisis. We're trying to get out of the
OL,11,Fcrisis onto a sustainable footing."
OL,13,FWork on a new #200 million emergency
OL,14,Fcare building is still going ahead, as
OL,15,Fis a new treatment centre and a
OL,16,Fcommunity diagnostics hub in the
OL,17,Fcentre of Plymouth.
